RESTful API for Order Management with MongoDB Integration

This project is a scalable and high-performing RESTful API for managing orders and customer information. Built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, it features CRUD operations for orders and customer data, JWT-based authentication, Swagger documentation, and extensibility. With a separate OrdersDAO module for MongoDB interactions, this API provides a strong foundation for building web applications.
